title: Ranked Rewards for Twisted Treeline?
body:
Hey peeps.

I've been looking online for a while and I've been confused and misinformed about this topic. It matters because I worked to get Gold 5 in Ranked Flex Twisted Treeline and I'm wondering if I get season end rewards for it. I've searched multiple websites and found nothing. If anyone could help me out that'd be greatly appreciated.

replies.body: Not sure!  We haven't announced any rewards for the current season.  I'm not sure when, but traditionally we've done it towards the end of a season.  Bookmark our [News](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) page and hang tight until then!
There were Rewards the last Season too, so yes there is i guess.
